Intellij
--> add plugin for copilot from settings --> plugins --> marketplace --> search for copilot --> install
--> restart intellij
--> login to github account
--> create a new java project

--> copilot suuggestions--> ghost code
--> some times copilot has multiple suggesstions - to navigate through suggesstions  - Alt + [ or Alt + ]
--> to accept the suggestion - Tab
--> to accept one word at a time ctrl + right arrow
--> to accept one line at a time ctrl + alt + right arrow
--> to see all the suggestions - Ctrl + Enter

-- we can write comments on the file to generate the code suggesstions by copilot

--ctrl+shift+c for opening copilot chat
--Agent for editing the class

